flowchart TD
  Reset[Reset / Boot ROM] --> Bootloader[Bootloader and image validation]
  Bootloader --> App[Application entry]
  App --> Drivers[Peripheral drivers]
  Drivers --> ISR[Interrupt handlers]
  Drivers --> DMA[DMA descriptors and buffers]
  App --> Tasks[FreeRTOS tasks]
  Tasks --> Telemetry[MQTT / serial telemetry]
  Tasks --> Storage[NVS / calibration storage]
  Tasks --> Validation[Validation hooks and benchmark probes]
